# English for simulation embed (keco-studio)

- The iframe shell under `src/app/(dashboard)/simulation-system/` and `SidebarSimulationSystemEntry` are part of the Keco dashboard: use **English** for user-visible strings, `title` attributes, Suspense fallbacks, and **comments** in these files.
- The full simulation UI lives in the sibling repo **`keco-simulation`**; keep terminology aligned (e.g. “Simulation system”, “Battle simulator”, “Battle skills”).

For the rest of keco-studio, follow `.cursor/rules/compatibility-modular-english-i18n.mdc` (product copy elsewhere may follow existing locale rules).
